    <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  Route a document to the correct structure constructor based on the <computeroutput>structure_type</computeroutput> parameter, enabling runtime selection of document structure representations. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class allows to construct structure from any document according to the available list of structure constructors. The list of structure constructors and names of structure types for them is set via the class constructor. Each structure type defines some specific document representation, which is retrieved via the corresponding structure constructor. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
